        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=48504&amp;TOPIC_ID=5747&amp;FORUM_ID=3&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=Necromancer+Game+Guides&amp;Topic_Title=Necro+Epic+Walkthrough&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Here's the original...</P><P>1.Head to Nektulos Forest and find the female NPC by the river loc -1000, -700 <BR>2. Head to Lake Rathe and find Kazen Facae loc 340 -1600 <BR>3. Kill Sir Edwin Motte (level 33 paladin). He is easiest to catch in tavern by the docks in East Freeport where he is on a rotation with the Tumpy Irontoe. <BR>4. Bring head of Motte to Kazen and recieve a Symbol of the Appretice <BR>5. Bring Symbol of the Appretice to the DE in Nektulos Forest, she'll return to you Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice <BR>6. Go to Najena and camp FBR and when you get it go to Nektulos Forest and give FBR to DE female and get some moss <BR>7. Head to Lake Rathe & give moss and Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice to Kazens apprentice, Emkel. Get Symbol of the Serpant. <BR>8. Go to Swamp of No Hope and find Ssessthrass loc 3800 1600 give him Symbol of the Serpant, receive Scaled Symbol of the Serpant. <BR>9. Head to Chardok. Kill Royal Herbalist and loot Manisi Herb (found on way to overking area, right before the secret door which leads to overking room). <BR>10. Go back to Ssessthrass and give him Scaled Symbol of the Serpant and herb, and he'll return Refined Manisi Herb. <BR>11. Head to Lake Rathe and give Emkel Refined Manisi Herb, he will give you Symbol of Testing. <BR>12. Have about 12-15 people ready (clerics and tanks are a must) and give Symbol of Testing to Kazen. 3 mobs will spawn. Kill these, last drops symbol of Insanity. <BR>13. Go to Timorous Deep, give Symbol of Insanity to Drendico Metalbones (near where evil raft drops you off, on hill) and he gives you his journal. <BR>14. Gather Cloak of Spiroc Feathers (quest in Sky), Eye of Innoruuk, and Blood of Cazic Thule. Bring all 3 along with Drendico's journal to Timorous deep. Give to Drendico, he returns to you a PREPARED REAGENT BOX. <BR>15. Take PREPARED REAGENT BOX to Kazen, and give to him...you get back a TOME OF INSTRUCTION. <BR>16. Go to Plane of Sky, give Thunder Spirit Princess 3pp. Then Clear isle to 3rd (Gorgalosk) isle. <BR>17. Give Gkzzallk the TOME OF INSTRUCTION. You get back GKZZALLK IN A BOX. (no battle.) <BR>18. Go to lake Rathe, give Kazel GKZZALLK IN A BOX. (no battle) Get back Scythe of the Shadowed Soul. DONE!. </P><P><BR>Here's my version of the Sky on part...</P><P>1)	Bind yourself and a Wizard/Druid at docks in NRo. (Prep)</P><P>2)	Gate everyone up to PoA.  </P><P>3)	Buy Key of Veshan from Key Master.  This is the key to the Quest Den.</P><P>4)	Give the Princess the 3pp before killing her to move to island 2.  This spawns Gkzallk on Grogalosk Island.</P><P>5)	Kill Azerak’s until a Silver disc drops off Isle 2. (Azarack Island)</P><P>6)	Kill Gorgalask's, and Spirited Harpies until a Spiroc feathers (one item, named plural) drop (Grogalosk Island)</P><P>7)	Kill Keeper of Souls for Black Silk Cape (*Isle 4, see farming below – Pegasus Isle).  </P><P>8)	Once you have all cloak quest parts, get killed on Isle 4 (Pegasus Island) (not duel, death).  ** Note 2</P><P>9)	Rez back and loot everything but ONE item, leaving corpse there.  Gate with a Wiz back to Island 1.</P><P>10)	Buy Key to Quest Isle and finish Cloak quest (Quest Isle).  Use Key of Veshan on other ring on Island 1.  Go to Drakis Bloodcaster ask him “Who is Jzil”.  Give book he gives you right back to him.  This spawns Jzil.  Give Jzil Black Silk Cape, Silver Disc, Sporic feathers (only one feather), receive Cape.  </P><P>11)	Gate to NRo with Wizard/Druid and do turn in of Cloak, Eye, Blood and Journal to Drendico – get Prepared Reagent Box. </P><P>12)	Gate to SK (from Wizard/Druid, run to LR and take Box to Kazen (Lake Rathe) Get Tome Of Instruction.  Bind yourself to Lake Rathe.  </P><P>13)	Get Rez back to corpse on Pegasus Island.  Wait for rez effects to fade, get SOW, cast Harmshield or QvoX and jump/run off finger SW edge of Pegasus Island that overlaps Gorgalask Island.  Give Gkzzallk Tome of Instruction and get Gkzallk In A Box.   (can switch with death on Island 4, rez to Island 4 and then SOW, Harm Shield, run/jump to Island 3 for turn in).  </P><P>14)	Self Gate to LR, turn in Gkzallk In a Box to Kazen get Duck.</P><P>*Keeper is farmed by killing ONE Pegasus or Griffon.  This causes Nottap Ekim to spawn on island 4.  When he de-spawns the Keeper should spawn in 80 minutes.  Assuming you only killed the ONE mob so far and Keeper is now up, kill ONLY the Keeper, wait for Sirran to de-spawn.  Restart cycle again…pull another mob from island 4, kill it, this causes the Keeper cycle to restart.  </P><P>** Second option is to summon corpse onto Island 1, create a key corpse and then use keys and invisibility to get to Gkzallk. </P><P>** Third Option is to get a key to the Monk Quest island.  Use the Katta Sword climbing trick.  HS and jump to Gkzallk Island.  </P><P><BR><center><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" target="_blank">Kuotat Smith</a><BR><s>Warlock</s> Witch<BR>Mithaniel Marr </center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

